  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >             <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099380/extras/babe5e8577aa4d663f8bbb2e8616f010.avif?t=1730405746\" width=508 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099380/extras/864d34c858d80c0ea103b4e4f8d0c8ca.poster.avif?t=1730405746\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099380/extras/864d34c858d80c0ea103b4e4f8d0c8ca.webm?t=1730405746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099380/extras/864d34c858d80c0ea103b4e4f8d0c8ca.mp4?t=1730405746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This is Frights</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find your way out of an old cavern filled with mysteries and a story untold. Find the crystals, give them to the spirit's voice, and she promised to get you back home!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >           <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099380/extras/eafe9fd6912e3614d09a5e000b15639e.avif?t=1730405746\" width=508 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You only need your keyboard. If an elephant is afraid of a mouse, so should you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Z: Select</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >X: Cancel</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left and Right Arrows: Turn Around</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up and Down Arrows: Move</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shift: Sprint</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099380/extras/135fb3867cd7a9cc2a45b3ec7038d492.avif?t=1730405746\" width=508 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099380/extras/1bfa7b6441d28f33a18f9fa17b6b01b1.poster.avif?t=1730405746\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099380/extras/1bfa7b6441d28f33a18f9fa17b6b01b1.webm?t=1730405746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099380/extras/1bfa7b6441d28f33a18f9fa17b6b01b1.mp4?t=1730405746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Yes.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But Toga will help you find your way back home!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be weary of the goat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visit our website for more news!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
